text: Obba may refer to: * Obba (town), an ancient town and former bishopric in the Roman province of Africa, now a Latin Catholic titular see * Oba (goddess), a Yoruba goddess ; Biology * Obba (fungus), a fungus genus in the order Polyporales * Obba (gastropod), a genus of land snail in the family Camaenidae * Obba, a synonym for Ugia, a genus of moths ; People * Obba Babatundé (born 1950), American stage and movie actor * Hatem Obba (born 1991), Tunisian volleyball player == See also == * Oba (disambiguation)
title: Obba
